Rapper Ad-Libs (rapper_adlibs) — Fair Use Notice

The audio clips in this pack are short artist "ad-lib" vocal sounds sourced from
therapboard.com. They are included here solely for personal, non-commercial use
as event sounds within the peon-ping / CESP ecosystem.

Each ad-lib remains the property of its respective artist and rights holder. No
ownership is claimed over any of the source recordings. This pack is not endorsed
by, affiliated with, or licensed by any of the artists featured or by
therapboard.com.

This pack is provided for personal use only. It may not be redistributed, sold,
or used for any commercial purpose. If you are a rights holder and want a clip
removed, open an issue on the pack repository.

The pack manifest (openpeon.json), filenames, and event mapping are released
under CC0-1.0 (public domain) by the pack author.
